Class BaseRegexFilter

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileExtFilter, FileNameFilter, FilePathFilter, TitleFilter

    public abstract class BaseRegexFilter
extends Filter
    Base filter that accepts a regular expression as the filter value. A base class can simply call match(String in) to determine a match.
